Sabse pehle urlModel.js
✅ 1. URL Model
Fields:

originalUrl
shortCode
clicks
user (ObjectId)
expiresAt (optional)
createdAt
updatedAt

✅ 2. urlController.js
Functions:

createShortUrl
redirectUrl
getMyUrls
deleteUrl

✅ 3. urlRoute.js
Routes:

POST    /url/shorten
GET     /url/my-urls
GET     /url/:shortCode
DELETE  /url/:id

✅ 4. Short Code Generator

Ek utility function jo unique code generate kare.

Example:

aB8kP2
Xz92Lm
kL7nQa

✅ 5. Redirect Logic

Flow:

GET /abc123
      │
      ▼
Find shortCode
      │
      ▼
clicks++
      │
      ▼
Redirect to original URL

Phase 6: Analytics
✅ 6. Analytics

Per URL:

Total Clicks
Created At
Expires At

